title: The $100k Coach w/ Jon Berghoff
itunes:title: The $100k Coach w/ Jon Berghoff
description:
Episode 340 - Jon Berghoff was my very first mentor. I hired him when I was 19 and paid him $500 a month. He now charges $100k for a weekend. In this episode, we talk about how to change your life through asking the right questions and how to be a great parent. Check it out!
